---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="404 | Página no encontrada">
  <section class="min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center text-center py-20 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-xl">
      
      <span 
        class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl text-primary opacity-0 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]"
        style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"
      >
        error
      </span>

      <div class="relative inline-block mt-4">
        <h1 
          class="text-8xl font-display font-extrabold text-text-light dark:text-text-dark opacity-0 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]"
          style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"
        >
          404
        </h1>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center transform -rotate-45 z-[-1] opacity-0 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]" style="animation-delay: 0.25s;">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p 
        class="text-2xl mt-6 font-display font-medium text-text-light/90 dark:text-text-dark/90 opacity-0 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]"
        style="animation-delay: 0.3s;"
      >
        Vaya, la innovación nos llevó demasiado lejos.
      </p>
      
      <p 
        class="mt-4 text-text-light/70 dark:text-text-dark/70 opacity-0 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]"
        style="animation-delay: 0.4s;"
      >
        La página que buscas no existe. Quizá la automatización la ha optimizado fuera de nuestra vista.
      </p>
      
      <a 
        href="/" 
        class="mt-8 inline-flex h-12 min-w-[84px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-primary px-6 text-base font-bold leading-normal tracking-[0.015em] text-background-light hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all hover:scale-105 transform opacity-0 animate-[fade-in-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]"
        style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"
      >
        Volver al Inicio (Wiñay)
      </a>
      
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>